_sText:
<font color="#66CCFF">Map Info</font>
==
Build whatever you want in this minecraft style map.
You have 1 minute to build a base with 3x3 blocks, you can make holes by breaking a block of the wall, after 1 minute, you will choose a weapon and the bedrock wall will break.
The map has 50 spawns points, but i dont recommend to put this map when the server is full, because it may lag.
there's a limit of 110 walls. (sorry for my bad english)
<font color="#66CCFF">Fix version</font>
==
Lots of bugs fixed
